==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unequaled
<hw>Un*e"qualed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not equaled;
unmatched; unparalleled; unrivaled; exceeding; surpassing; -- in a good
or bad sense; <as>as, <ex>unequaled</ex> excellence; <ex>unequaled</ex>
ingratitude or baseness</as>.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>unequalled</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unequally</ent>⟦br⟧
